#Falafels #Health #PlantBased #Vegan #Health #Food

Ingredients for Falafel
1 bundle fresh parsley (2 cups chopped)
3 large cloves garlic
1 large lemon (2 1/2 Tbsp juice)
1/2 tsp sea salt
1/2 tsp onion powder
1 1/4 tsp cumin
15-ounce chickpeas, soaked and drained
1/2 cup pecan meal
 
The Mediterranean inspired quinoa salad 
3 cups of Quinoa cooked
1TBSP of lemon/ lime juice
1/2 cup of chopped red onions
1 TBSP of chopped parsley
1/4 cup of chopped Kalamata olives
1 cup chopped cherry tomatoes
1 TBSP of olive oil
Salt to taste
One clove of garlic minced

Tzatziki sauce 
1 block firm/ Silken tofu (16 oz) ( Or use 16oz  plain yogurt)
3 cloves garlic, peeled
1 medium lemon, juiced
1/4 cup fresh chopped dill or 2 TSP dried dill
1/2 cup water
1/4 teaspoon salt
½- 1 cucumber, grated
